@startuml
title Feature 011. Order history and order details sequence

actor "Покупатель/партнер" as User
participant "Web-shell /order/order-history" as UI
participant "OrderHistoryController" as Controller
participant "OrderHistoryService" as Service
participant "OrderHistoryRepository" as Repo
participant "Cart context" as Cart
participant "Audit trail" as Audit

User -> UI : Открывает список истории заказов
UI -> Controller : GET /api/order/order-history?filters
Controller -> Service : searchHistory(currentUser, filters, page)
Service -> Repo : findOwnedOrders(currentUser.id, filters, page)
Repo --> Service : OrderHistoryPage
Service --> Controller : page with statuses, warnings, summary items
Controller --> UI : OrderHistoryPageResponse
UI --> User : Показывает список, фильтры, поиск и статусы

User -> UI : Открывает детали ORD-011-MAIN
UI -> Controller : GET /api/order/order-history/ORD-011-MAIN
Controller -> Service : getDetails(currentUser, orderNumber)
Service -> Repo : findOwnedOrderDetails(orderNumber, currentUser.id)
alt Заказ принадлежит пользователю
  Repo --> Service : OrderDetails
  Service --> Controller : Details with items, delivery, payment, events, actions
  Controller --> UI : OrderDetailsResponse
  UI --> User : Показывает детали, timeline, предупреждения и действия
else Чужой заказ
  Repo --> Service : not owned
  Service -> Audit : record security denial
  Service --> Controller : STR_MNEMO_ORDER_HISTORY_ACCESS_DENIED
  Controller --> UI : 403 ErrorResponse
  UI --> User : Безопасное состояние доступа запрещено
end

User -> UI : Выбирает repeat order
UI -> Controller : POST /api/order/order-history/ORD-011-MAIN/repeat
Controller -> Service : repeatOrder(currentUser, orderNumber, idempotencyKey)
Service -> Repo : get repeatable lines and order type
Service -> Cart : add allowed lines to MAIN or SUPPLEMENTARY cart
Cart --> Service : added/rejected lines
Service -> Audit : record repeat order action
Service --> Controller : RepeatOrderResponse
Controller --> UI : repeat result
UI --> User : Показывает добавленные и недоступные позиции
@enduml
